---
description: Trigger design-craft for product UI/UX and frontend design-quality work.
globs:
  - "**/*.{css,scss,tsx,jsx,mdx}"
alwaysApply: false
---

Use `design-craft` for product UI/UX, visual taste critique, design-system
enforcement, UI polish, motion review, responsive/browser validation, and
frontend craft.

Do not use it for backend-only logic, database-only migrations, pure algorithms,
CLI-only tools, or non-visual refactors unless UI quality is affected.

Authority order: live runtime and browser evidence, project rules/README,
project `DESIGN.md` or equivalent style authority, then `design-craft`
references. Do not generic-redesign a project over its existing product context.
